    "body": "That's how **Python** behave:\n\n```\n>>> '%e hi there' % (50/3)\n'1.600000e+01 hi there'\n```\n\nHere using `Hi there` instead of 3, you are just doing string formatting.\n\nWhat you want is the following:\n\n```\n>>> '%.2e' % (50/3)\n'1.60e+01'\n```\n\nSo with the precision magic (which is just syntactic sugar)\n\n```\nIn [1]: %precision %.2e\nOut[1]: '%.2e'\n\nIn [2]: 5/3\nOut[2]: 1.67e+00\n```\n"
  },
